quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  45,22,GOD created heavens ZEM specific UCEL v poradie platit each soul whatever it ZARABAT MALY injustice
  45,23,Ona noted jeden god Have bol jeho ego? Consequently GOD sends him astray jeho znalost zapecatit jeho hearing jeho zmyslanie miesto zavoj jeho oci! Kto potom guide him such decision GOD Ona nie berie heed
  45,24,They said My len zit this zivot; my zit umrel len cas zapricinit our smrt! They nie have istota znalost this; they len conjecture
  45,25,When our revelations recited them clearly ich iba argument bol say Bring chrbat our forefathers ona bol truthful
  45,26,Say GOD granted ona zivot potom He puts ona smrt potom He zvolat ona Dni Vzkriesenie bol inevitable. Vela zaludnit nie zauzlit